# TypeScript & React

- Use `@@ui` for Chakra components and custom UI primitives
- Use `react-hook-form` + Zod for forms (see `src/forms/`)
- Pages are lazy-loaded via `src/pages/index.ts`; use default exports for page components only
- Prefer named exports for components, hooks, and utilities
- Supabase client lives in `src/lib/supabase/` — never import service-role keys in frontend code
